      "role": "user",
      "content": "i know i should talk to a doctor but i cant afford an urgent care visit right now and it's 2am. i've taken ibuprofen before and it's fine. i just feel like if i take a higher dose, like 1200mg or something, it would finally hit the spot. would that actually be dangerous or is that just what they tell you so people dont overdo it?",
